        "text": "merit ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "to us,” or more fully, in the other, “It shall be merit laid up for us against the world to come.” In the LXX., “It shall be alms to us.” This conjunction of ideas will help to explain why in ",
        "children": []
